<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> rāyalu ratna 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> prithivi rājyaṁ 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> pavitru 
<lb n="4-11"/><ce>lines are completely damaged</ce>
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Aṁtta <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/>vaṭṭunnu sōma <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kālamaṁdu 
<lb n="14"/>hiraṇyōdaka dā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kaṁgānu rā 
<lb n="15" break="no"/><unclear>ju</unclear>gāriki puṇyaṁgānu trivācakaṁgā dhāravō 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>si Istimi <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> yī puṇyānku yavvaru tappi 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>nānu tamatallitaṁḍrādula gōbrā 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>hmani vadhiṁccina pāpāna bōvu 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>vāru svadattā dviguṇaṁ 
<lb n="20"/>puṇyaṁ paradattānu pā 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="21" break="no"/>lanaṁ paradattāpahārēṇa 
<lb n="22"/>svadattaṁ niṣphalaṁ bhavēt śrī śrī śrī 
</p>

